          "description": "When another non-conjured ally on the battlefield is defeated or sacrificed by any source, there is a chance to add another Gyurelle to next in line of allied reinforcements, so long as this unit is not defeated or sacrificed at the same time and there are not already 3 Conjured Earth allies named Gyurelle between the battlefield and allied reinforcements. The chance of adding another Gyurelle increases depending on the size of this unit's team, up to 100% when this unit's last ally is defeated (so long as that ally was not conjured). The Level, Limit Breaks, Awakenings, Boosts, Potential, Mastery, Weapon and Accessory of Gyurelles added by this skill will match this unit."
